    "title": "Gross transfers from Centre to states (all-India)",
    "description": "Total gross flow of resources from the Centre to all states before the Centre claws back loan repayments and interest (Item IV = Item I devolution + Item II grants + Item III gross loans). The 'headline' transfer figure citizens encounter in budget commentary. Net transfer (`fiscal/national_centre_transfers_total`) is gross minus repayments / interest.",
