      "state_pct": 0,
      "source": "definition (own vs centrally-transferred)"
    },
    "implementing_authority": "centre",
    "methodology_vintage": "RBI State Finances: A Study of Budgets, Appendix Table 2; cached file mtime 2026-05-11T14:50:50Z",
    "notes": "Source: RBI 'State Finances: A Study of Budgets', Appendix Table 2, Item IV 'Gross Transfer (I+II+III)'. Nominal ₹ Crore. Same dedupe and qualifier rules as the other national_centre_* indicators."
